narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, the work is manageable and the tests/quizzes are fine as long as you study.
It's a requirement. That is all.
It's what you would probably expect from a language course. Each professor does things a little differently though, so find a prof. that you like.Oscar comes highly recommended from me.
I would recommend it although I take it ue to requirements
Take it if you have to or if you like languages. Not a very fun class for anyone who isn't good at picking up new languages. No harder than L1 or L2.
If you are interested in getting better at speaking Spanish take this course. If you are just trying to pass lang requirements then look elsewhere.
Only to fulfill language requirement or if they want to major in a language.
